東帝汶國會宣布，未來在全體會議中，每個月至少將有一次以[葡萄牙語](http://easttimorlegal.blogspot.com/2011/04/on-
use-of-portuguese-in-
national.html?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+EastTimorLawJusticeBulletin+%28East+Timor+Law+&+Justice+Bulletin%29
"http://easttimorlegal.blogspot.com/2011/04/on-use-of-portuguese-in-
national.html?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+EastTimorLawJusticeBulletin+%28East+Timor+Law+&+Justice+Bulletin%29")開會，一位部落客表示，「這就像是澳洲、美國或英國國會以日文公告新法」。

